metadata.name: Can you give yourself to the sea?
metadata.description:
Up.....and down, with every breathe. 

At first the fleeting feeling of control scares me, makes me want to call for help. 

'Kicking harder', as if it would turn this liquid to solid and allow me to walk to land.

Breathe in, breathe out. 

The wind picks up and soon the boat will be out of earshot. 

Do you fight...

Can you give yourself to the sea?


1462 × 2047 | 300 dpi 

A moment of realization in the process.
